profile.name: Women's Gold Medalists Rio 2016
profile.blurb: Inspiring girls & young women. Women's Gold medalists is an illustrated book & poster of all the women who won gold medals at the Rio Olympics. It is a juxtaposition of sport, women and design as well as a documented celebration of female achievement.
